See the file COPYING for more information.

Requirements:

  LG TV with RS-232 interface

Description:

  Control LG TV via RS-232

Features:

 - auto powercontrol
 - auto volumecontrol
 - auto switch 3D mode (3dcontrol plugin needed)

Configuration:

 OSD - Auto TV Power On / Off
          enable/disable TV Powercontrol switch on/off TV

 OSD - Set User inactive if TV is Off
          control TV Powerstatus to set user inactive

 OSD - LG Volume Control
          enable/disable TV Volumecontrol

 OSD - LG Basevolume
          TV default Volumelevel if VDR volume is lower than 
          the increaselevel option

 OSD - VDR Increaselevel

 Commandline - "-d  DEV  --device=DEV"
          Set user define serialport default = /dev/ttyUSB0

aviable commands via plugin service:

 - LG_Disable3D
 - LG_SideBySide3D
 - LG_SideBySide3DLR
 - LG_TopBottom3D
 - LG_CheckBoard3D
 - LG_FrameSequential3D
 - LG_Converted2D
 - LG_SetVolume
 - LG_GetVolume
 - LG_PowerOff
 - LG_PowerOn
 - LG_TogglePower
 - LG_GetCurrentPowerStatus
 - LG_ToggleMute
 - LG_IsMute
 - LG_ToggleRemoteLocked
 - LG_IsRemoteLocked

aviable commands via SVDRP:

 - LGTV [ ON | OFF ]
 - LG3D [ OFF | SBS | SBSRL | SBSLR | TB | FS | CB | 2D ]
 - LVOL [ <number> | + | - | MUTE ]
 - LGAV [ AV ]
